attributes.Long form description: The student is to assemble the chair. The student holds both legs first and then screws the bolt and hex nut by hand. Next, he flips the legs, tightens the hex nut using a wrench, and then flips the legs again to attach the seat. Using a black screwdriver, he screws all four screws and saddle washers on each leg. Lastly, he stands the chair on the table.

attributes.Transcription: We'll now be assembling the small chair from IKEA.
so please go ahead and assemble it.
